In his latest video Scott Manley flew New Horizons to Pluto. What mod is the spacecraft from?

<iframe width="480" height="270" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Rb2lc2fLXpw?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="true"></iframe>

Remote Tech, AIES, and Mechjeb from what I see. He's also using Procedural Parts, Procedural Farrings, RSS, and RO.
